{
  "text": "In this paper, we propose to replace the classical direct visual servoing [CITATION_1] , as described above, by a new scheme based on a convolutional neural network (CNN). The network is trained to estimate the relative pose between the current and reference image. Given an image input I(r) and the reference image I0, let the output of the network be:",
